Author:
Vol / Page: 56 Vict. 30/178
Edition:
Quote: "Factory" or "creamery" shall mean aplace established for receiving the milkor cream of cows from the public for thepurpose of manufacturing the same or anyportion of the same into butter orcheese, or both, as the case may be.
